issue.title: [CF 15] Unresponsive Frames
issue.body:
Submitted Via

Curse Client 4.0.1.98, Microsoft Windows NT 5.1.2600 Service Pack 3

Installed Version

TellMeWhen1.2.5b1

Description

Tell me when's frames cannot be moved or even interacted with beyond hghlightng them. You are unable to change the buff options, move the bars, anything. Further, there is no longer a menu for tmw in the interface addons section.
